'''Meen-tris''' was an [[Eickarie]] family, that made up [[Sav-ro]] clan and tribe [[Hu-shi-crive]] on the planter [[Kariek]] during the [[New Republic era]]. For centuries the family guarded the secret of the third watch tower entrance to the [[Cro-sla-trie]] fortress. Until family member [[Su-mil]] used it to help the [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Imperial Stormtroopers]] of [[Aurek Company]] gain access.<ref name="CSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

